 here business of sieving sand until I got another job - hand carting and afterwards. I got a - in a place in Cable Street - taking orders out to - with a hand cart. Pulling a hand cart round - round Park Lane, Walton - all round different shops. All diff
erent kinds of - and s-ou'wester, uniforms and - things like that.
