 the two shilling bonus provided that you went - you went to work to time - you got to work to time and you weren't fined. You were f
ined a case of - if you were late one morning you were fined sixpence or twice then you were fined a shilling or - you done anything wrong in the works the foreman could turn round and fine you sixpence. Or back - any back }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
